00:19:27,430 --> 00:19:29,960
there are any other ways?

288
00:19:30,190 --> 00:19:31,150
How about

289
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:34,030
leaving your portfolio here.

290
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:36,390
If you haven't received any messages
till tomorrow,

291
00:19:36,670 --> 00:19:38,150
you are out of chance.

292
00:19:39,550 --> 00:19:41,960
Okay, thank you, Ms. Sun.

293
00:19:43,310 --> 00:19:45,360
