294
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:46,760
Thanks.

295
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:56,840
Xianxian

296
00:19:57,150 --> 00:19:58,120
Shadi

297
00:19:58,390 --> 00:19:59,760
What took you so long?

298
00:20:01,270 --> 00:20:03,080
I'm too busy lately.

299
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:06,360
Stay with me tonight.

300
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:09,670
But there will be a roll-call at eleven.

301
00:20:09,670 --> 00:20:10,720
I gotta come back.

302
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:12,760
It's been a long time.

303
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:14,360
Don't you want to spend

304
00:20:14,510 --> 00:20:17,190
a night of girls?

305
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:22,240
Alright. You beat me.

306
00:20:26,880 --> 00:20:29,430
I went to the hospital to visit Zhou
a few days ago.

307
00:20:29,840 --> 00:20:30,880
So

308
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:33,190
concentrate in your major.

309
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:35,640
Just come to me if

310
00:20:36,190 --> 00:20:37,640
you need money.

311
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:40,240
It's okay. I can do it.

312
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:42,720
Mind your health.

313
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:44,390
You know what,

314
00:20:44,910 --> 00:20:46,430
the selection of exchange students

315
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:47,790
has already started.

316
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,150
It won't not be a problem for you
to study abroad

317
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:51,720
once you finish this project.

318
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:53,510
Okay.

319
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:55,080
One more thing.

320
00:20:56,910 --> 00:20:59,480
Ding Xian came to me a few days ago,

321
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:02,760
saying that she found something she is more interested in

322
00:21:03,080 --> 00:21:04,840
and she wanted to quit the group.

323
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:05,880
I said yes.

324
00:21:11,150 --> 00:21:12,270
It's great.

325
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:14,600
I had no idea

326
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:16,270
so many things happened

327
00:21:16,430 --> 00:21:18,550
between you and Zhou Siyue.

328
00:21:19,430 --> 00:21:21,310
What's that senior's name exactly?

329
00:21:21,310 --> 00:21:22,120
Which department does she in?

330
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:23,840
I can meet her for you.

331
00:21:24,390 --> 00:21:25,880
You missed the point.

332
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:28,360
It has already happened.

333
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:30,190
I'm not thinking of him anymore.

334
00:21:33,080 --> 00:21:33,910
You know what?

335
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:35,760
I've been always thinking that

336
00:21:36,150 --> 00:21:38,790
it must be you to stay with Zhou Siyue.

337
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:43,240
What about now?

338
00:21:44,550 --> 00:21:46,080
Now I'm confused too.

339
00:21:47,120 --> 00:21:48,840
Relationship between lovers
has become so complicated

340
00:21:49,190 --> 00:21:52,430
since we grow up.

341
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,910
What shall we have for lunch?

342
00:22:04,190 --> 00:22:05,670
It's up to you.

343
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:08,360
I always want to eat...

344
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:09,310
What?

345
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:10,840
Mr. Charming.

346
00:22:36,190 --> 00:22:37,550
What's fun in the phone?

347
00:22:37,910 --> 00:22:39,030
Even ignored Mr. Charming.

348
00:22:39,760 --> 00:22:41,240
I'm waiting for the call from the press.

349
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:43,760
So you and Zhou Siyue...

350
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:45,720
Don't mention him.

351
00:22:47,190 --> 00:22:48,550
Did you cut off the thread of love?

352
00:22:49,790 --> 00:22:52,150
Yeah, now I am ascetic.

353
00:22:52,150 --> 00:22:53,600
I only concerned about my career.

354
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:55,000
It can't be better.

355
00:22:55,760 --> 00:22:56,790
Ding Xian

356
00:22:58,390 --> 00:22:59,430
I finally got you.

357
00:22:59,840 --> 00:23:01,150
What's the matter, President?

358
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:03,480
Ms. Sun from the Dream Journey Press
has come to you.

359
00:23:04,790 --> 00:23:06,270
Do I get the chance for the competition?

360
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:08,640
No, she's going to sign a contract with you.

361
00:23:10,790 --> 00:23:11,720
Sign a contract?

362
00:23:12,550 --> 00:23:13,600
For real?

363
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:14,640
Yes.

364
00:23:16,600 --> 00:23:17,670
I knew it.

365
00:23:18,190 --> 00:23:19,910
Why doesn't she come to me herself?

366
00:23:20,190 --> 00:23:21,670
She said you were in a rush,

367
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,510
with no contact left.

368
00:23:23,510 --> 00:23:24,510
How could she come to you herself?

369
00:23:25,550 --> 00:23:26,510
Right.

370
00:23:38,080 --> 00:23:40,360
Is this the popular novel The Shadow

371
00:23:40,360 --> 00:23:42,150
on the Lijiang Literary website?

372
00:23:42,840 --> 00:23:45,550
Do you want me to adapt it into a comic?

373
00:23:45,910 --> 00:23:46,790
What do you think?

374
00:23:47,150 --> 00:23:48,030
Do you have the confidence?

375
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:52,310
The contract has already been drawn up.

376
00:23:53,310 --> 00:23:54,640
Take a look.

377
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:58,150
If there's no argument about the price,

378
00:23:58,790 --> 00:24:01,390
we can set about the next step.

379
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:11,150
May I take it back and have a close look?

380
00:24:11,430 --> 00:24:12,310
Of course.

381
00:24:13,120 --> 00:24:14,190
But there are still

382
00:24:15,360 --> 00:24:17,760
lots of candidates for this project.

383
00:24:18,080 --> 00:24:19,000
I'm a little worried.

384
00:24:19,270 --> 00:24:20,670
You know, time waits for no one.

385
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,720
Thanks for your trust.

386
00:24:26,390 --> 00:24:28,550
I ought to keep faith with you too.

387
00:24:45,150 --> 00:24:46,670
Mr. Su, this is the sponsoring proposal

388
00:24:46,670 --> 00:24:48,760
of the Comics Club of Huaqing University.

389
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:50,550
The contact information is on the last page.

390
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:53,120
Okay, thank you.

391
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:08,120
Hello.

392
00:25:08,120 --> 00:25:09,000
Is this Xing Lufei?

393
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,430
Yes.

394
00:25:11,390 --> 00:25:12,760
I'm not sure if you remember me or not.

395
00:25:13,190 --> 00:25:15,390
I'm Su Bocong, from Chima Technology.

396
00:25:16,150 --> 00:25:18,150
Would you like to

397
00:25:18,430 --> 00:25:19,600
go out for a dinner today?

398
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:23,120
I happen to have a few high school mates

399
00:25:23,120 --> 00:25:24,190
from Huaqing University.

400
00:25:24,550 --> 00:25:26,270
We'd like to gather with you.

401
00:25:26,270 --> 00:25:27,840
You may know them.

402
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:33,720
You have not uttered a single word since you came back.

403
00:25:34,030 --> 00:25:35,640
It's not like you, Mr. Zhou.

404
00:25:37,150 --> 00:25:38,080
Was I being too mean

405
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:40,430
the other day?

406
00:25:42,080 --> 00:25:43,190
Which day?

407
00:25:44,670 --> 00:25:45,760
Don't play dumb with me.

408
00:25:48,190 --> 00:25:49,390
You were not only being mean.

409
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:50,960
You were being a jerk.

410
00:25:59,360 --> 00:26:00,840
I just wanted her to

411
00:26:00,840 --> 00:26:02,390
do something she likes.

412
00:26:03,550 --> 00:26:05,910
She shouldn't sacrifice herself for me.

413
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:08,670
Do you feel regret?

414
00:26:09,310 --> 00:26:11,270
She may not talk to you now even if you come to her.

415
00:26:11,910 --> 00:26:12,760
You deserve it.

416
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:13,790
You dug yourself a grave.

417
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:37,550
I thought you don't like dinner parties.

418
00:26:39,430 --> 00:26:41,030
But this one, I must go.

419
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,640
Bocong, sorry to keep you waiting.

420
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:48,480
You are here.

421
00:26:49,550 --> 00:26:51,550
Hello,
I'm the president of the Comics Club, Ji Hang.

422
00:26:51,790 --> 00:26:54,000
I'm Su Bocong, nice to meet you.

423
00:26:54,430 --> 00:26:55,360
Please be seated.

424
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:56,480
Xianxian, sit here.

425
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:03,600
Su

426
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:07,240
I didn't know you are the sponsor.

427
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:09,600
Ding Xian

428
00:27:09,760 --> 00:27:11,880
If we know you two are this close,

429
00:27:12,080 --> 00:27:13,910
you'd be in charge of the sponsorship.

430
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:17,000
Where's Zhou Siyue?

431
00:27:19,270 --> 00:27:20,760
He's on the way.

432
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:27,910
We've just arrived.

433
00:27:28,150 --> 00:27:29,000
Have a seat here.

434
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:39,190
Zhou Siyue

435
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:40,550
It's been a long time.

436
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:42,600
Right, it's been a long time.

437
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:46,150
It seems you've known each other.

438
00:27:46,430 --> 00:27:48,030
No more introduction then.

439
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:50,790
Let's start to order now.

440
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,960
What would you like to eat?

441
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,720
Xianxian

442
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:59,030
What would you like to eat?

443
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:01,550
Zhou Siyue, this is for you.

444
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:04,120
Sorry to take your

445
00:28:04,120 --> 00:28:05,030
chocolates last time.

446
00:28:05,030 --> 00:28:06,790
I got you a same one.

447
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:09,270
Stop being mad at me.

448
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,550
Come on, let's eat up.

449
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:25,190
Bocong is so young and promising.

450
00:28:25,760 --> 00:28:27,150
You only graduated two years earlier than us,

451
00:28:27,390 --> 00:28:29,550
but you've already started to invest us.

452
00:28:30,310 --> 00:28:31,600
You are much more excellent.

453
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:33,190
I was just

454
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:35,030
being lucky to

455
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:36,790
be appreciated.

456
00:28:37,310 --> 00:28:38,360
You are too modest.

457
00:28:41,080 --> 00:28:42,000
Xianxian

458
00:28:42,310 --> 00:28:43,240
This Sour Soup Fish tastes

459
00:28:43,430 --> 00:28:45,000
similar to that in our hometown.

460
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:46,640
Have a try.

461
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:49,430
Ding Xian doesn't like sour things.

462
00:28:56,670 --> 00:28:57,960
Don't you like it anymore?

463
00:29:01,430 --> 00:29:02,430
I'll have a taste.

464
00:29:12,840 --> 00:29:13,720
How do you like it?

465
00:29:19,840 --> 00:29:21,030
Well, Bocong

466
00:29:21,600 --> 00:29:23,270
I am quite curious.

467
00:29:24,430 --> 00:29:25,390
For what?

468
00:29:26,640 --> 00:29:28,640
What's the relationship between

469
00:29:29,190 --> 00:29:30,880
you and our little sister Ding Xian?

470
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:37,880
My parents get on well with his family.

471
00:29:38,430 --> 00:29:40,550
So we've known each other since we were kids.

472
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:41,880
Grow up together.

473
00:29:42,080 --> 00:29:44,790
So you are childhood sweethearts.

474
00:29:47,310 --> 00:29:48,240
I mean it seems that

475
00:29:48,430 --> 00:29:50,360
Bocong has a crush on you.

476
00:29:54,360 --> 00:29:55,720
I do like her

477
00:29:58,670 --> 00:30:00,600
and I'm going to invite her

478
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:02,030
to my company when she graduates.

479
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:08,510
Of course, you're all

480
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:09,880
warmly welcomed.

481
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:13,430
Bocong, you are so nice to Xianxian.

482
00:30:20,190 --> 00:30:21,480
I need to go to the toilet.

483
00:30:25,550 --> 00:30:26,790
Excuse me.

484
00:30:27,430 --> 00:30:28,240
Help yourselves.

485
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:36,390
Zhou Siyue

486
00:30:51,270 --> 00:30:53,960
What are you going to say?

487
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:56,600
I like Ding Xian.

488
00:31:01,510 --> 00:31:02,430
So what?

489
00:31:04,240 --> 00:31:06,480
I like her since we were kids.

490
00:31:07,150 --> 00:31:08,880
I'll gradually make up the hurt

491
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:10,240
she got from you.

492
00:31:11,360 --> 00:31:13,720
I'm capable of giving her a better life.

493
00:31:14,670 --> 00:31:16,430
So please get away from her.

494
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:19,910
What's between her and me

495
00:31:20,880 --> 00:31:22,600
has nothing to do with you.

496
00:31:27,120 --> 00:31:29,270
Despite my relationship with Xianxian,

497
00:31:30,360 --> 00:31:32,270
I have promised Xianxian's parents

498
00:31:32,430 --> 00:31:33,640
to take care of her.

499
00:31:35,360 --> 00:31:37,840
So I'm responsible for her stuff.

500
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:39,790
Why don't you talk about your relationship?

501
00:31:40,910 --> 00:31:42,550
I'd like to know what kind of relationship

502
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:46,000
between you and Ding Xian.

503
00:31:51,190 --> 00:31:53,600
What about yours?

504
00:32:00,510 --> 00:32:03,240
No matter what relationship between us now,

505
00:32:05,310 --> 00:32:08,790
she will only be with me for her life.

506
00:32:21,310 --> 00:32:22,240
Xianxian

507
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:33,880
Ding Xian

508
00:32:35,720 --> 00:32:36,480
Ding Xian

509
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:42,550
Zhou Siyue, what else do you want?

510
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:44,600
I was being too harsh

511
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:47,120
to you the other day.

512
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:50,190
I'm so sorry.

513
00:32:52,430 --> 00:32:54,390
I didn't expect Mr. Zhou would apologize.

514
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:57,910
After that day,

515
00:32:59,150 --> 00:33:00,790
I've been thinking all the time.

516
00:33:02,600 --> 00:33:04,360
I can't imagine

517
00:33:04,760 --> 00:33:06,430
what my life will be

518
00:33:06,430 --> 00:33:07,790
without you.

519
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:10,480
Stop flattering yourself, Zhou Siyue.

520
00:33:11,080 --> 00:33:12,240
You have no right to

521
00:33:12,390 --> 00:33:14,190
decide the relationship between us,

522
00:33:14,510 --> 00:33:16,390
nor make decisions for me.

523
00:33:18,600 --> 00:33:20,880
I said you are not the center of my life any more.

524
00:33:21,080 --> 00:33:22,670
You don't need to make any explanations to me.

525
00:33:23,270 --> 00:33:24,150
Ding Xian

526
00:33:27,790 --> 00:33:29,150
Calm down please.

527
00:33:30,120 --> 00:33:30,670
Honestly...

528
00:33:30,670 --> 00:33:31,640
Calm down?

529
00:33:32,390 --> 00:33:33,190
You think I'm totally

530
00:33:33,190 --> 00:33:35,120
obsessed with you, right?

531
00:33:35,760 --> 00:33:37,960
Or is it fun to play me like a fool?

532
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:40,640
You just get used to having me

533
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:42,670
follow you all the time.

534
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:46,960
But I'm tired.

535
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:50,240
Let everything stop here.

536
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:24,310
Xianxian

537
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:28,880
Get in the car. I'll give you a ride.

538
00:34:41,989 --> 00:34:42,949
Xianxian

539
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:45,030
It seems the dishes today

540
00:34:45,030 --> 00:34:46,199
didn't suit your taste.

541
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:48,550
Would you like to eat something else?

542
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:51,840
Thank you, Su.

543
00:34:52,880 --> 00:34:53,880
I'm not hungry.

544
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,950
Have you heard

545
00:34:58,510 --> 00:34:59,680
what we said in the restaurant?

546
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:05,270
Only a part of it.

547
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:09,840
But it's enough.

548
00:35:13,160 --> 00:35:14,120
It is all over.

549
00:35:16,120 --> 00:35:17,840
I won't feel upset for him any longer.

550
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:23,470
How about I come back to Shen Hai with you in the New Year's vacation.

551
00:35:24,270 --> 00:35:25,360
I can also get some fresh air.

552
00:35:26,030 --> 00:35:28,400
I can't go with you.

553
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:30,880
I still have a Comicon to go in Huaicheng.

554
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:53,400
Kong Shadi

555
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:56,470
It's me.

556
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:03,840
Listen to me.

557
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:05,550
I just had a nightmare,

558
00:36:06,270 --> 00:36:07,750
in which Kong Shadi and I

559
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:09,950
were stuck in a rainforest.

560
00:36:10,160 --> 00:36:11,310
We were on a big tree,

561
00:36:11,640 --> 00:36:13,120
with lots of crocodiles below.

562
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:14,440
Then she said to me,

563
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:16,160
Song Ziqi, I will feed you to the crocodiles.

564
00:36:16,160 --> 00:36:18,750
And she pushed me off right away.

565
00:36:22,550 --> 00:36:23,470
So scary.

566
00:36:24,790 --> 00:36:25,920
Song Ziqi

567
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:26,990
I got one question for you.

568
00:36:28,080 --> 00:36:30,840
What would you do

569
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:34,200
if Kong Shadi disappears some day?

570
00:36:38,510 --> 00:36:40,680
Such a boring question.

571
00:37:10,080 --> 00:37:12,080
I've thought about it very clearly.

572
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:15,510
