578
00:37:29,600 --> 00:37:31,950
I'll find him

579
00:37:32,120 --> 00:37:33,880
wherever he goes.

580
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:36,640
I must know the answer.

581
00:37:38,990 --> 00:37:42,990
It's not that important to know the answer.

582
00:37:44,640 --> 00:37:47,360
