585
00:37:54,030 --> 00:37:55,550
I know I can't.

586
00:37:56,990 --> 00:37:58,310
I know I can't

587
00:37:58,470 --> 00:38:00,120
give up easily.

588
00:38:01,510 --> 00:38:02,600
And I can't help falling in love with him

589
00:38:03,310 --> 00:38:06,470
every time I see him.

590
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:09,920
But I have to tell myself

591
00:38:11,400 --> 00:38:13,600
to hang in as possible as I can.

592
00:38:14,030 --> 00:38:14,990
Alright.

593
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:18,440
I'm always here to support you.

594
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:20,160
Bye-bye.

595
00:38:20,270 --> 00:38:21,230
Bye.

596
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:41,600
Zhou Siyue, why have I become the one

597
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:43,600
who knows you the least?

598
00:38:44,270 --> 00:38:46,990
Why can't you just be honest with me?

599
00:38:50,470 --> 00:38:52,120
It has been four years, Zhou Siyue.

600
00:38:52,950 --> 00:38:54,920
Do you really think I haven't confirmed it myself?

601
00:38:55,680 --> 00:38:57,440
I have asked myself for a thousand times,

602
00:38:57,440 --> 00:38:59,080
am I fall in love with you,

603
00:39:00,160 --> 00:39:02,440
or it's just an illusion in puberty?

604
00:39:04,440 --> 00:39:05,360
The only thing I can

605
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:07,270
be sure in this world

606
00:39:09,310 --> 00:39:11,200
is my feelings toward you.

607
00:39:16,680 --> 00:39:17,990
You just get used to having me

608
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:19,790
follow you all the time.

609
00:39:21,080 --> 00:39:22,710
But I'm tired.

610
00:39:24,750 --> 00:39:26,270
We are over now.

611
00:40:02,230 --> 00:40:03,200
Hey, Xianxian.

612
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:04,160
Hey, Su.

613
00:40:04,790 --> 00:40:06,680
I got your present.

614
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:09,750
It's too valuable. I can't keep it.

615
00:40:10,080 --> 00:40:11,710
You must keep it.

616
00:40:11,990 --> 00:40:13,840
I knew you wouldn't accept it to my face.

617
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:15,470
So I asked someone to put it at your dorm.

618
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:18,600
If you feel apologetic,

619
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:22,510
draw more and better pictures with it.

620
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:23,880
Take it as a sort of investment.

621
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:28,080
Thank you.

622
00:40:29,030 --> 00:40:31,440
I'll save up to give you a birthday...

623
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,230
Xianxian

624
00:40:32,510 --> 00:40:33,510
I got another call.

625
00:40:33,640 --> 00:40:34,710
I gotta go.

626
00:40:35,030 --> 00:40:35,840
Okay.

627
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,200
Okay, see you.

628
00:40:38,310 --> 00:40:39,230
Bye-bye.

629
00:41:28,030 --> 00:41:29,160
Song Ziqi

630
00:41:42,750 --> 00:41:43,710
Hello?

631
00:41:44,990 --> 00:41:45,950
Where are you?

632
00:41:45,950 --> 00:41:46,990
Kong Shadi's around.

633
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:49,550
I'm worried she may follow you to find me.

634
00:41:49,790 --> 00:41:51,840
So I just come out and hide for a while.

635
00:41:52,440 --> 00:41:53,640
Good for you.

636
00:41:53,750 --> 00:41:54,710
I gotta go.

637
00:42:59,710 --> 00:43:00,680
Song Ziqi

638
00:43:01,600 --> 00:43:03,360
Miss, you got the wrong person.

639
00:43:03,750 --> 00:43:05,200
Who's Song Ziqi?

640
00:43:14,120 --> 00:43:14,950
Song Ziqi!

641
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:24,990
Song Ziqi, stand still.

642
00:43:25,200 --> 00:43:26,270
Wait for me.

643
00:43:38,400 --> 00:43:39,470
Hey, Shasha.

644
00:43:39,950 --> 00:43:40,950
Hey, Ding Xian.

645
00:43:41,120 --> 00:43:42,550
Zhou Siyue is a big liar.

646
00:43:43,880 --> 00:43:45,030
What did he do?

647
00:43:45,230 --> 00:43:47,160
He lied to me that he didn't know where Song Ziqi is.

648
00:43:47,270 --> 00:43:49,030
He's been right here.

649
00:43:50,080 --> 00:43:51,360
How did you know?

650
00:43:52,750 --> 00:43:54,030
I just saw him.

651
00:43:54,230 --> 00:43:55,200
I'm so mad.

652
00:43:56,080 --> 00:43:57,160
I'm going to your school later.

653
00:43:57,310 --> 00:43:58,230
Get out now.

654
00:43:58,880 --> 00:44:00,600
Wait a second. I'm on my way.

655
00:44:02,640 --> 00:44:04,400
What are we doing here exactly?

656
00:44:04,550 --> 00:44:05,790
I'm going to follow Siyue.

657
00:44:05,950 --> 00:44:07,360
He knows for sure where Song Ziqi is.

658
00:44:07,510 --> 00:44:08,440
I can surely find that jerk

659
00:44:08,440 --> 00:44:10,200
by following him.

660
00:44:10,600 --> 00:44:12,680
You can do it yourself. Why do you call me here?

661
00:44:12,920 --> 00:44:14,200
Aren't you my bestie?

662
00:44:14,360 --> 00:44:15,640
Come alone with me, please.

663
00:44:20,200 --> 00:44:22,470
What? How did she find you?

664
00:44:22,710 --> 00:44:23,640
How could I know she would go to

665
00:44:23,790 --> 00:44:25,600
the bookstore, bro?

666
00:44:26,030 --> 00:44:26,990
Bookstore?

667
00:44:27,550 --> 00:44:29,990
I didn't expect you would go to the bookstore either.

668
00:44:30,270 --> 00:44:31,750
You two are indeed a perfect match.

669
00:44:31,880 --> 00:44:33,470
Stop joking with me.

670
00:44:33,600 --> 00:44:34,880
Just tell me what should I do.

671
00:44:35,680 --> 00:44:36,750
Where are you right now?

672
00:44:36,950 --> 00:44:38,030
I'm at the basement.

673
00:44:38,550 --> 00:44:39,950
Come back now.

674
00:44:40,160 --> 00:44:41,080
I'm frightened.

675
00:44:42,080 --> 00:44:43,680
Alright, don't be frightened.

676
00:44:44,080 --> 00:44:45,230
I'm on my way.

677
00:44:48,310 --> 00:44:49,360
Don't be frightened.

678
00:44:50,030 --> 00:44:51,360
He is going back.

679
00:44:52,840 --> 00:44:53,880
Let's go, let's go.

680
00:45:12,680 --> 00:45:13,640
He's looking over here.

681
00:45:14,360 --> 00:45:15,270
It's okay.

682
00:45:16,200 --> 00:45:17,470
Will he find us?

683
00:45:17,790 --> 00:45:18,680
No, he won't.

684
00:45:21,470 --> 00:45:22,400
Have a look now.

685
00:45:22,840 --> 00:45:23,680
Let me see.

686
00:45:28,920 --> 00:45:29,840
He's gone.

687
00:45:39,950 --> 00:45:40,990
Didn't she follow you?

688
00:45:41,640 --> 00:45:42,550
She did,

689
00:45:42,840 --> 00:45:43,790
with Ding Xian.

690
00:45:45,400 --> 00:45:46,270
Take it easy.

691
00:45:47,030 --> 00:45:47,990
I saw them.

692
00:45:48,310 --> 00:45:49,920
They won't come here.

693
00:45:52,030 --> 00:45:52,990
Is it here?

694
00:45:53,160 --> 00:45:55,680
Well, are you sure you've got rid of them?

695
00:45:55,990 --> 00:45:57,510
Are you definitely sure...

696
00:45:57,510 --> 00:45:58,950
I thought I heard Song Ziqi's voice.

697
00:45:58,950 --> 00:45:59,950
You need to take this seriously.

698
00:45:59,950 --> 00:46:01,270
I'll be dead if she

699
00:46:01,270 --> 00:46:02,680
